ing: 2 (3 ounce) packages instant pistachio pudding mix
des: "Very simple and quick, perfect for a barbecue dessert or any time of the year. Best served the same day it is made. Serve topped with whipped cream."
ins: Stir milk and pudding mix together in a large bowl. Chill until set, about 1 hour. Stir pineapple tidbits, walnuts, marshmallows, and coconut into pudding. Spread pudding mixture into prepared graham cracker crusts.
